Available Tools: get_page_views | get_unique_visitors | get_session_duration | get_bounce_rate
Call Schema: { "func_call": "string", "url": "string", "from_date": "string", "to_date": "string", "granularity": "hourly|daily|weekly|monthly" }
Response Schema: { "url": "string", "period": "string", "views": number, "unique_visitors": number, "avg_session_seconds": number, "bounce_rate": number }
---
Question: What were the view counts for the autumn footwear collection page during September?
Call: { "func_call": "get_page_views", "url": "https://store.fashionhub.net/collections/autumn-boots", "from_date": "2023-09-01", "to_date": "2023-09-30", "granularity": "daily" }
Response: { "url": "https://store.fashionhub.net/collections/autumn-boots", "period": "2023-09-01 to 2023-09-30", "views": 28400, "unique_visitors": 19200, "avg_session_seconds": 165, "bounce_rate": 0.38 }

